  <summary>Tool for Flatpak Steam which allows custom launch options and 3rd party applications</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A tool for use with the Flatpak Steam client which allows customising start tools and options for games quickly on the fly.</p>
    <p>By using a versatile configuration structure it is both easy to set up and flexible.</p>
    <p>Please be aware this does not work on Steam Deck. To find out how to use on Steam Deck please visit the wiki.</p>
  </description>
